= Where to read more

- `note/main.typ` --- math (manifolds, retraction, batched einsum, Riemannian Adam).
- GitHub Pages #link("https://nzy1997.github.io/ParametricDFT.jl/dev/training/")[Training] --- API reference autogenerated from source docstrings.
- GitHub Pages #link("https://nzy1997.github.io/ParametricDFT.jl/dev/performance/")[Performance] --- measured speed-ups over a Manopt baseline; batch-size decision rule.
- `examples/basis_demo.jl` --- full QFT / Entangled / TEBD comparison on MNIST or QuickDraw (heavier; requires dataset download).
- `examples/circuit_visualization.jl` --- generate PNG circuit diagrams for any basis.
